OL,5, Uber Eats is facing a backlash after   
OL,6, its Super Bowl advert appeared to make 
OL,7, light of a man having an allergic      
OL,8, reaction to peanut butter.             
OL,10,FThe Food Allergy Research & Education  
OL,11,F(FARE) charity said it was "surprised  
OL,12,Fand disappointed" to see the company   
OL,13,Fuse allergies as a joke.               
OL,15,FOne person, himself allergic to        
OL,16,Fpeanuts, called the ad "disgusting,    
OL,17,Ftone-deaf and completely unnecessary". 
OL,19,FThe BBC has approached Uber Eats for a 
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
